            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "香港科技探索1月每日訂單交易按月升13.9%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">HKTVmall母公司香港科技探索(01137)今早公布，香港電子商貿業務1月平均每日訂單總商品交易額(GMV)按月升13.9%至2380萬元，按年升3%，帶動每月訂單總商品交易額達7.39億元，按月升13.9%，按年升3.1%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"香港科技探索將軍澳總部\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/20250325_FI_HKTV.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"香港科技探索將軍澳總部\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/20250325_FI_HKTV.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">香港科技探索將軍澳總部</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">獨立客戶數目上升 6.1%至 64萬名，而每月活躍獨立設備數目則維持穩定於156.3萬名。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">集團香港電子商貿業務平均每日訂單數量50900張，按月升11.4%，按年升13.9%；平均訂單值468元，按月升2.2%，按年則跌9.5%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15667550-%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e7%a7%91%e6%8a%80%e6%8e%a2%e7%b4%a21%e6%9c%88%e6%af%8f%e6%97%a5%e8%a8%82%e5%96%ae%e4%ba%a4%e6%98%93%e6%8c%89%e6%9c%88%e5%8d%8713-9",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241113_FI_source-web_01137-2.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-02-16 17:26:42",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
